</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="161" pageNumber="764" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="161.[1446,2652,299,566]" pageId="161" pageNumber="764">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1446,1683,335,369]" pageId="161" pageNumber="764">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Bunting’s Thicket Rat is assumed to be nocturnal and arboreal, as other members of genus.
